LibWinpos Release Notes

1. Commit changes in Git:

git commit -a -m "Release version 0.1.1"
git tag -s -f -m "Release 0.1.1" v0.1.1 <gpg password>
git push && git push --tags

2. Do post release version bump in `RELEASE`, `CMakeLists.txt` and `meson.build`

3. Commit trivial changes:

git commit -a -m "trivial: post release version bump"
git push
